metadata.name: Lucid in Dreamland
metadata.description:
Lucid in Dreamland is an art collaboration between illustrator Lei Melendres with gravure model/photographer/cosplayer Natsuki Jiro. This is the first time he's ever created an artwork that has a slightly more mature content which he combines with his usual playful characters and elements.

The goal of the artist was to create a theme similar to Alice in Wonderland but with a psychedelic/trippy twist by showing what she was experiencing inside her head while having a really good trip.

The artist promises to create another piece to add to this collection every time a piece is sold until they reach a maximum of (12) artworks for the whole collaboration since Natsuki has already created several photos meant for the series.

You can check out 
Lei Melendres at https://linktr.ee/leimelendres
Natsuki Jiro's at https://linktr.ee/natsukijiro

Thank you for your support! More to come!
